SUMMARY:theHunter: Call of the Wild | Ep. 47 - The Highlands Belong to the
 Haggis
DESCRIPTION:We return to the wild landscapes of theHunter: Call of the
 Wild for more tracking, patience, and questionable aim. The Highlands are
 calling - and I'm fairly certain something is watching us already.\n
 Experience an atmospheric hunting game like no other in this realistic and
 visually breathtaking open world. Immerse yourself in the atmospheric
 single player campaign, or share the ultimate hunting experience with
 friends.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7y37UiBOMys
CATEGORIES:theHunter: Call of the Wild
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-22502211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260203T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260301T173500Z
DTSTART:20260224T213000Z
DTEND:20260224T233000Z
SUMMARY:Star Trek Online | Ep. 10 - Perhaps Today Is a Good Day to Explore
DESCRIPTION:Back into Star Trek Online for more exploration, unexpected
 encounters, and boldly going because someone has to. In Star Trek Online,
 the Star Trek universe appears for the first time on a truly massive
 scale. Players take the captain's chair as they command their own starship
 and crew. Explore strange new worlds, seek out new life and new
 civilizations, and boldly go where no one has gone before.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D43g1N6aq5E
CATEGORIES:Star Trek Online
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-22512211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260204T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260301T173500Z
DTSTART:20260225T213000Z
DTEND:20260225T233000Z
SUMMARY:Sniper Elite V2 Remastered | Ep. 2 - Mittelwerk Facility
DESCRIPTION:Precision, patience, and cinematic slow-mo returns in Sniper
 Elite V2 Remastered. The mission continues - and yes, the shots will be
 carefully lined up. In the dark days of the end of World War 2 amidst the
 ruins of Berlin, one bullet can change history... Elite sniper Karl
 Fairburne returns to the front line in the remaster of this award-winning
 stealth-action experience. Packed with new features, contemporary visuals
 and definitive content.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=08kqAR6rAXQ
CATEGORIES:Sniper Elite V2 Remastered
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-22522211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260205T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260301T173500Z
DTSTART:20260226T213000Z
DTEND:20260226T233000Z
SUMMARY:Star Trek: Voyager - Across the Unknown | Ep. 2 - Diplomacy First.
 Unless They're Rude
DESCRIPTION:Our journey inspired by Star Trek: Voyager continues.
 Exploration, negotiation... and possibly photon torpedoes if diplomacy
 fails. Star Trek: Voyager - Across the Unknown is a story-driven survival
 strategy game in which the fate of the iconic starship is in your hands.
 Take the helm, manage the ship and resources, and make difficult
 decisions. Will you be able to bring home the ship and its crew?
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8oLle30MPb4
CATEGORIES:Star Trek: Voyager - Across the Unknown
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-22542211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260207T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260301T173500Z
DTSTART:20260228T213000Z
DTEND:20260228T233000Z
SUMMARY:Red Dead Redemption II | Ep. 6 - The West Ain't Kind to Anyone
DESCRIPTION:Back into the chaos of Fallout 4. The park is still dangerous.
 I am still underprepared. We're going anyway. Arthur Morgan and the Van
 der Linde Gang are outlaws on the run. With federal agents and bounty
 hunters massing on their heels, the gang must rob, steal, and fight their
 way across the rugged heartland in order to survive.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5eBHrcR28IQ
CATEGORIES:Red Dead Redemption II
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
