SUMMARY:Euro Truck Simulator 2 | Ep. 6 - Taking the Scenic Route Across
 Europe
DESCRIPTION:Time to relax behind the wheel in Euro Truck Simulator 2.
 Smooth roads, beautiful views... and absolutely no wrong turns. Probably.
 Travel across Europe as king of the road, a trucker who delivers important
 cargo across impressive distances! With dozens of cities to explore, your
 endurance, skill and speed will all be pushed to their limits.
URL:https://www.twitch.tv/dr_ravenholm
CATEGORIES:Euro Truck Simulator 2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
